MALALANE- In the early hours of the morning a pedestrian was killed on the road between the Nkomazi Plaza and Alzu Petroport.  According to the spokesman  for the Department of Community Safety, Security and Liaison Moeti Mmusi the pedestrian was hit by a car which dragged him some distance before driving off.  Mmusi indicated  that police were still continuing with their investigation.This is a developing story, Lowvelder will update you as more information comes to light.